node.text:
The wait is over. “Shame On You” drops tonight!

Pre-save “Shame On You" (link in bio), share the pic, and tag me.  I’m adding 100 people that do that to my close friend's list. 

1 person  will get handwritten lyrics to the song.  7

📸 @deeds_art

#thefarrises 
#myAngelina

 📸 @visual_thought
